when (

 inner join STUDENTADMINISTRATIVEENROLMENT_FOLDER saf on saf.IDENTITYEMP = emp.IDENTITYEMP
 inner join STUDENTADMINISTRATIV sa on sa.idstudentadministrativ = saf.IDSTUDENTADMINISTRATIV

 and sa.KWENROLMENTSTATUS = 'bcfaabac-e283-43b3-8fdc-a69f00f3c2ac'
 and ( select COUNT(*) from ADMINENROLMENTSESSIO aes2 
 where aes.DTSESSIONSTART = aes2.DTSESSIONSTART

 end

FORMAT(ISNULL((CASE WHEN REFWEIGHTING IS NULL THEN numUnitPrice * numQuantity ELSE 
	( 
		CASE 
			WHEN KWWEIGHTINGTYPE IS NULL THEN 0
			WHEN KWWEIGHTINGUNIT IS NULL THEN 0
			WHEN NUMQUANTITY IS NULL THEN 0
			WHEN NUMUNITPRICE IS NULL THEN 0
			WHEN KWWEIGHTINGTYPE = '9a9dacd2-ce4f-4c4d-87b3-a70500c22981' THEN 
				(
				/*remise */ 
				CASE 
				/*pourcentage */
					WHEN KWWEIGHTINGUNIT = '50ca40ec-6bac-45e7-a00d-a70500c83b22' THEN NUMQUANTITY * NUMUNITPRICE * (1 - NUMWEIGHTING/100) /*montant */
					WHEN KWWEIGHTINGUNIT = '61cff7c8-ad96-4e10-8240-a70500c83b26' THEN NUMQUANTITY * NUMUNITPRICE - NUMWEIGHTING
				ELSE 0
				END
				)
			WHEN KWWEIGHTINGTYPE = '4d2acc3a-ff87-4f1a-92c6-a70500c22994' THEN 
				(
				/*majoration */ 
				CASE 
				/*pourcentage */
					WHEN KWWEIGHTINGUNIT = '50ca40ec-6bac-45e7-a00d-a70500c83b22' THEN NUMQUANTITY * NUMUNITPRICE * (1 + NUMWEIGHTING/100) /*montant */
					WHEN KWWEIGHTINGUNIT = '61cff7c8-ad96-4e10-8240-a70500c83b26' THEN NUMQUANTITY * NUMUNITPRICE + NUMWEIGHTING
				ELSE 0
				END
				)
		ELSE 0
		END)
END), 0), 'C', 'fr-FR')

FORMAT(ISNULL(SUM(
	(CASE WHEN ISNULL(NUMQUANTITY, 0) = 0 THEN 0
	 WHEN ISNULL(NUMUNITPRICE, 0) = 0 THEN 0
	 ELSE
	 (CASE WHEN REFWEIGHTING IS NULL THEN numUnitPrice * numQuantity ELSE

			 WHEN '61cff7c8-ad96-4e10-8240-a70500c83b26' THEN NUMQUANTITY * NUMUNITPRICE - NUMWEIGHTING /* montant */

			(CASE KWWEIGHTINGUNIT

IF ISNULL((SELECT COUNT(*) FROM STUDENTADMINISTRATIV WHERE IDSTUDENTADMINISTRATIV = '%ID_IA%' AND STRADMINENROLMENTNUMBER = 'strAdminEnrolmentNumber'), 0) > 0
BEGIN
	UPDATE STUDENTADMINISTRATIV
	SET STRADMINENROLMENTNUMBER =
		s.strCode 
		+ '-' 
		+ RIGHT('000' + CAST(ISNULL((
			SELECT COUNT(*) FROM STUDENTADMINISTRATIV sa1
			INNER JOIN AESESSIONOFAE_LINK ael1 ON ael1.ENTITY1_IDSTUDENTADMINISTRATIV = sa1.IDSTUDENTADMINISTRATIV
			LEFT JOIN AESESSIONOFAE_LINK ael2 ON ael2.ENTITY2_IDADMINENROLMENTSESSIO = ael1.ENTITY2_IDADMINENROLMENTSESSIO
			INNER JOIN STUDENTADMINISTRATIV sa2 ON sa2.IDSTUDENTADMINISTRATIV = ael2.ENTITY1_IDSTUDENTADMINISTRATIV
			WHERE sa1.IDSTUDENTADMINISTRATIV = '%ID_IA%'
			AND CAST(sa2.CREATEDDATE AS DATE) <= sa1.CREATEDDATE 
			AND (sa2.CREATEDDATE < sa1.CREATEDDATE
				 OR (sa2.CREATEDDATE = sa1.CREATEDDATE AND RIGHT('0000000000' + sa2.strIDOP, 10) < RIGHT('0000000000' + sa1.strIDOP, 10)))
		  ), 0) + 1 AS NVARCHAR(255)), 4)
	FROM ADMINENROLMENTSESSIO s
	INNER JOIN AESESSIONOFAE_LINK ael ON ael.ENTITY2_IDADMINENROLMENTSESSIO = s.IDADMINENROLMENTSESSIO AND ael.ENTITY1_IDSTUDENTADMINISTRATIV = '%ID_IA%'
	WHERE IDSTUDENTADMINISTRATIV = '%ID_IA%' AND STRADMINENROLMENTNUMBER = 'strAdminEnrolmentNumber'
END

DECLARE @idItem UNIQUEIDENTIFIER;
DECLARE @TempItems TABLE (idItem UNIQUEIDENTIFIER, idIA UNIQUEIDENTIFIER);

INSERT INTO @TempItems (idItem, idIA) SELECT entity2_idItem, '%ID_IA%' FROM AdminEnrolmentItem_link WHERE entity1_idstudentAdministrativ = '%ID_IA%' and isdeleted = 0

WHILE (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM @TempItems WHERE idIA = '%ID_IA%') > 0
BEGIN

	SET @idItem = (SELECT TOP 1 idItem from @TempItems WHERE idIA = '%ID_IA%');

	UPDATE item 
	SET refSalesPriceBase = spb.idSalesPriceBase,
		numUnitPrice = (CASE ISNULL(numSelectedPrice, 0) WHEN 0 THEN spb.numUnitPrice ELSE numSelectedPrice END),
		numQuantity = (CASE ISNULL(kwUnit.textvalue_frfr, 'Stagiaire') WHEN 'Stagiaire' THEN 1 ELSE NULL END)
	FROM AdminEnrolmentItem_link ai_link
		LEFT JOIN studentAdministrativ ae ON ae.idstudentAdministrativ = ai_link.entity1_idstudentAdministrativ
		LEFT JOIN StudentAdministrativeEnrolment_folder aef ON aef.IDSTUDENTADMINISTRATIV = ae.IDSTUDENTADMINISTRATIV
		LEFT JOIN EntityEmp e ON e.idEntityEmp = aef.idEntityEmp
/*
		LEFT JOIN Country nat1 ON nat1.IdCountry = e.refNationality
		LEFT JOIN keywordvalue kwUEnat1 ON kwUEnat1.idkeywordvalue = nat1.kwUE
		LEFT JOIN Country nat2 ON nat2.IdCountry = e.refDoubleNationality
		LEFT JOIN keywordvalue kwUEnat2 ON kwUEnat2.idkeywordvalue = nat2.kwUE
*/
		LEFT JOIN AESessionofAE_link aes_link ON aes_link.entity1_idstudentAdministrativ = ae.idstudentAdministrativ
		LEFT JOIN adminenrolmentsessio aes ON aes.idadminenrolmentsessio = aes_link.entity2_idadminenrolmentsessio
		LEFT JOIN AdminEnrolmentSession_folder aes_folder ON aes_folder.idadminenrolmentsessio = aes_link.entity2_idadminenrolmentsessio
		LEFT JOIN ItemOfItemType_folder iit_folder ON iit_folder.iditem = ai_link.entity2_iditem
		LEFT JOIN (
			SalesPriceBase spb 
			INNER JOIN SALESPRICEBASEDEGREE_LINK spbd ON spbd.Entity1_IdSalesPriceBase = spb.idSalesPriceBase
		) ON spb.refItemType = iit_folder.idItemType 
		AND (spb.kwRegistrationRegime IS NULL OR spb.kwRegistrationRegime = ae.kwRegistrationRegime)
		AND (spb.kwReEnrollment IS NULL OR spb.kwReEnrollment = ae.kwReEnrollment)
		AND (SELECT Value FROM keywordvalue WHERE idkeywordvalue = spb.kwDeprecated) = 0
		AND spbd.Entity2_IdDegree = aes_folder.IdDegree
		LEFT JOIN keywordvalue kwUnit ON kwUnit.idkeywordvalue = spb.kwUnit

	WHERE ai_link.entity2_iditem = @idItem
		AND item.idItem = @idItem

	DELETE FROM @TempItems WHERE idItem = @idItem;
END

DECLARE @idItem UNIQUEIDENTIFIER;
DECLARE @TempItemsWeight TABLE (idItem UNIQUEIDENTIFIER, idIA UNIQUEIDENTIFIER);

INSERT INTO @TempItemsWeight (idItem, idIA) SELECT entity2_idItem, '%ID_IA%' FROM AdminEnrolmentItem_link WHERE entity1_idstudentAdministrativ = '%ID_IA%'

WHILE (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM @TempItemsWeight WHERE idIA = '%ID_IA%') > 0
BEGIN

	SET @idItem = (SELECT TOP 1 idItem from @TempItemsWeight WHERE idIA = '%ID_IA%');

	UPDATE Item
	SET refWeighting  = wb.idWeightingbase,
		numWeighting = wb.numWeighting,
		kwWeightingUnit = wb.kwUnit,
		kwWeightingType = wb.kwWeightingType
	FROM Item
	 LEFT JOIN AdminEnrolmentItem_link ai_link ON ai_link.entity2_iditem = Item.idItem
	 LEFT JOIN studentAdministrativ ae ON ae.idstudentAdministrativ = ai_link.entity1_idstudentAdministrativ
	 LEFT JOIN weightingBase wb 
	 
	 ON wb.refSalesPriceBase = Item.refSalesPriceBase 
	 AND (wb.kwAffiliation IS NULL OR wb.kwAffiliation = ae.kwAffiliation)
	 AND (wb.kwContribution IS NULL OR (SELECT Value FROM keywordvalue WHERE idkeywordvalue = wb.kwContribution) = ISNULL((SELECT Value FROM keywordvalue WHERE idkeywordvalue = ae.kwContribution), 2))
	 AND (wb.kwScholarshipHolder IS NULL OR (SELECT Value FROM keywordvalue WHERE idkeywordvalue = wb.kwScholarshipHolder) = ISNULL((SELECT Value FROM keywordvalue WHERE idkeywordvalue = ae.kwScholarshipHolder), 2))

	 
	WHERE Item.idItem = @idItem

	DELETE FROM @TempItemsWeight WHERE idItem = @idItem;
END

UPDATE Rate
SET strCode = 'TFF' + 
	CASE
		WHEN
			(SELECT COUNT(*)
			FROM Rate va
			WHERE left(va.strCode,3) = 'TFF') = 0
			THEN '0001'
		ELSE RIGHT(
					'0000' + CAST(
									(
										SELECT MAX(
													right(va2.strCode,4)
													) + 1
										FROM Rate va2
										WHERE left(va2.strCode,3) = 'TFF')AS NVARCHAR(255)), 4)
	END
FROM Rate va0
WHERE va0.IDRATE='%ID_RATE%'

UPDATE studentAdministrativ
SET kwAffiliation = (CASE WHEN tmp.age BETWEEN 16 AND 28 AND tmp.job > 0 THEN
							(CASE tmp.job WHEN 19 THEN maintien.idKeyWordValue
								  ELSE
									(CASE WHEN tmp.age <= 20 THEN
											(CASE WHEN tmp.job >= 16 THEN maintien.idKeyWordValue
												  WHEN tmp.job BETWEEN 6 AND 15.5 THEN
													(CASE tmp.age WHEN 20 THEN secuEtud.idKeyWordValue ELSE maintien.idKeyWordValue END)
												  ELSE secuEtud.idKeyWordValue END)
										  ELSE secuEtud.idKeyWordValue END)
								  END)
						  ELSE pasAffil.idKeyWordValue END)
FROM KeyWordValue maintien, KeyWordValue secuEtud, KeyWordValue pasAffil,
(
	SELECT sa.IdStudentAdministrativ AS 'id', ISNULL(job.value, 0) as 'job', ISNULL(bourse.value, 2) as 'bourse',
		   FLOOR(DATEDIFF(DAY, e.dtbirthdate, aes.dtSessionEnd)/365.242199) AS 'age'
	FROM ENTITYEMP e
	LEFT OUTER JOIN KeyWordValue job ON job.idKeyWordValue = e.kwParentJobOfAttachment
	INNER JOIN StudentAdministrativeEnrolment_FOLDER saef ON saef.identityemp = e.identityemp AND saef.IdStudentAdministrativ = '%ID_IA%'
	INNER JOIN studentAdministrativ sa ON sa.IdStudentAdministrativ = saef.IdStudentAdministrativ
	LEFT OUTER JOIN KeyWordValue bourse ON bourse.idKeyWordValue = sa.kwScholarshipHolder
	INNER JOIN AESessionOfAE_LINK asoal ON asoal.entity1_IdStudentAdministrativ = saef.IdStudentAdministrativ
	INNER JOIN AdminEnrolmentSessio aes ON aes.IdAdminEnrolmentSessio = asoal.entity2_IdAdminEnrolmentSessio
) tmp
WHERE tmp.id = IdStudentAdministrativ
AND maintien.entityCode = 'studentAdministrativ' AND maintien.fieldCode = 'kwAffiliation' AND maintien.code = '2'
AND secuEtud.entityCode = 'studentAdministrativ' AND secuEtud.fieldCode = 'kwAffiliation' AND secuEtud.code = '1'
AND pasAffil.entityCode = 'studentAdministrativ' AND pasAffil.fieldCode = 'kwAffiliation' AND pasAffil.code = '3'

Name.fr-FR: Calcul pour l'affectation auto du champ Statut d'affiliation

Sql.Value:
UPDATE studentAdministrativ
SET kwAffiliationAge = (CASE WHEN tmp.age BETWEEN 16 AND 28 AND tmp.job > 0 THEN
						  (CASE WHEN tmp.job = 19 THEN vSNCF.idKeyWordValue
								ELSE
									(CASE WHEN tmp.age BETWEEN 16 AND 19 THEN 
											(CASE WHEN tmp.job < 6 THEN v1619S.idKeyWordValue
												  ELSE v1619R.idKeyWordValue END)
										  WHEN tmp.age = 20 THEN
											(CASE WHEN tmp.job < 16 THEN 
													(CASE tmp.bourse WHEN 2 THEN v20S.idKeyWordValue ELSE v20SB.idKeyWordValue END)
												  ELSE v20R.idKeyWordValue END)
										  WHEN tmp.age BETWEEN 21 AND 28 THEN
											(CASE tmp.bourse WHEN 2 THEN v2128.idKeyWordValue ELSE v2128SB.idKeyWordValue END)
										  END)
								END)
						  WHEN tmp.age > 28 and tmp.job > 0 THEN vSup28.idKeyWordValue
						  ELSE NULL END)
FROM KeyWordValue v1619S, KeyWordValue v1619R, KeyWordValue v20S, KeyWordValue v20SB, KeyWordValue v20R, KeyWordValue v2128, KeyWordValue v2128SB,
	 KeyWordValue vSup28, KeyWordValue vSNCF,
(
	SELECT sa.IdStudentAdministrativ AS 'id', ISNULL(job.value, 0) as 'job', ISNULL(bourse.value, 2) as 'bourse',
		   FLOOR(DATEDIFF(DAY, e.dtbirthdate, aes.dtSessionEnd)/365.242199) AS 'age'
	FROM ENTITYEMP e
	LEFT OUTER JOIN KeyWordValue job ON job.idKeyWordValue = e.kwParentJobOfAttachment
	INNER JOIN StudentAdministrativeEnrolment_FOLDER saef ON saef.identityemp = e.identityemp AND saef.IdStudentAdministrativ = '%ID_IA%'
	INNER JOIN studentAdministrativ sa ON sa.IdStudentAdministrativ = saef.IdStudentAdministrativ
	LEFT OUTER JOIN KeyWordValue bourse ON bourse.idKeyWordValue = sa.kwScholarshipHolder
	INNER JOIN AESessionOfAE_LINK asoal ON asoal.entity1_IdStudentAdministrativ = saef.IdStudentAdministrativ
	INNER JOIN AdminEnrolmentSessio aes ON aes.IdAdminEnrolmentSessio = asoal.entity2_IdAdminEnrolmentSessio
) tmp
WHERE tmp.id = IdStudentAdministrativ
AND v1619S.entityCode = 'studentAdministrativ' AND v1619S.fieldCode = 'kwAffiliationAge' AND v1619S.code = '1619S'
AND v1619R.entityCode = 'studentAdministrativ' AND v1619R.fieldCode = 'kwAffiliationAge' AND v1619R.code = '1619R'
AND v20S.entityCode = 'studentAdministrativ' AND v20S.fieldCode = 'kwAffiliationAge' AND v20S.code = '20S'
AND v20SB.entityCode = 'studentAdministrativ' AND v20SB.fieldCode = 'kwAffiliationAge' AND v20SB.code = '20SB'
AND v20R.entityCode = 'studentAdministrativ' AND v20R.fieldCode = 'kwAffiliationAge' AND v20R.code = '20R'
AND v2128.entityCode = 'studentAdministrativ' AND v2128.fieldCode = 'kwAffiliationAge' AND v2128.code = '2128'
AND v2128SB.entityCode = 'studentAdministrativ' AND v2128SB.fieldCode = 'kwAffiliationAge' AND v2128SB.code = '2128SB'
AND vSup28.entityCode = 'studentAdministrativ' AND vSup28.fieldCode = 'kwAffiliationAge' AND vSup28.code = '+28'
AND vSNCF.entityCode = 'studentAdministrativ' AND vSNCF.fieldCode = 'kwAffiliationAge' AND vSNCF.code = 'SNCF'

- l'IA qui déclenche le flux
- les Documents à renseigner associés au Programme et Cours dont est issue la Session d'IA de l'IA, qui ne sont pas supprimés, avec Obsolète = False (ou non renseigné)

Ajout des relations Document de l'IA entre :
- l'IA qui déclenche le flux
- les Documents à renseigner associés au Programme et Cours dont est issue la Session d'IA de l'IA, qui ne sont pas supprimés, avec Obsolète = False (ou non renseigné)

Seules les relations qui n'existent pas déjà sont créées.

Sql.Value:
DECLARE @temp TABLE
	(IDStudentAdministrativ UniqueIdentifier, IDDocumentsToFill UniqueIdentifier, ID UniqueIdentifier, IDFilledDocuments UniqueIdentifier) 
INSERT INTO @temp
	SELECT '%ID_IA%', dtfdl.ENTITY1_IDDocumentsToFill, newId(), newId()
	FROM AESessionOfAE_Link aesael
	INNER JOIN AdminEnrolmentSession_Folder aesf ON aesf.IDAdminEnrolmentSessio = aesael.ENTITY2_IDAdminEnrolmentSessio AND aesf.IsDeleted = 0
	INNER JOIN DocumentsToFillDegree_Link dtfdl ON dtfdl.ENTITY2_IDDegree = aesf.IDDegree AND dtfdl.IsDeleted = 0
	INNER JOIN DocumentsToFill dtf ON dtf.IDDocumentsToFill = dtfdl.ENTITY1_IDDocumentsToFill AND dtf.IsDeleted = 0
	LEFT OUTER JOIN KeyWordValue kwDeprecated ON kwDeprecated.IdKeyWordValue = dtf.kwDeprecated
	WHERE aesael.ENTITY1_IDStudentAdministrativ = '%ID_IA%' AND aesael.IsDeleted = 0 AND ISNULL(kwDeprecated.Code, 'False') = 'False'
	AND NOT EXISTS (
		SELECT * FROM FilledDocuments_Link
		WHERE ENTITY1_IDStudentAdministrativ = '%ID_IA%' AND ENTITY2_IDDocumentsToFill = dtfdl.ENTITY1_IDDocumentsToFill AND IsDeleted = 0)

INSERT INTO FilledDocuments
	(IdOwner, ValidityStart, CreatedDate, IsDeleted, IDFilledDocuments)
SELECT 'CE3ECFB7-CA2C-4FD6-A87B-1EB11C7A7E13', GETDATE(), GETDATE(), 0, IDFilledDocuments
FROM @temp

INSERT INTO FilledDocuments_Link
	(ENTITY1_IDStudentAdministrativ, ENTITY2_IDDocumentsToFill, ID, IDOwner, ValidityStart, CreatedDate, IsDeleted, IDFilledDocuments)
SELECT IDStudentAdministrativ, IDDocumentsToFill, ID, 'CE3ECFB7-CA2C-4FD6-A87B-1EB11C7A7E13', GETDATE(), GETDATE(), 0, IDFilledDocuments
FROM @temp

UPDATE studentAdministrativ
SET kwContribution = (CASE WHEN tmp.kwAffiliation = '1' AND tmp.age >= 20 AND tmp.bourse = 2 AND tmp.kwAffiliation2 = '2' THEN oui.idKeyWordValue
						   ELSE non.idKeyWordValue END)
FROM KeyWordValue oui, KeyWordValue non,
(
	SELECT sa.IdStudentAdministrativ AS 'id', ISNULL(kwAffiliation.code, '3') as kwAffiliation, ISNULL(kwAffiliation2.code, '2') as kwAffiliation2,
		   ISNULL(kwForceContribution.value, 0) as kwForceContribution, ISNULL(bourse.value, 2) as 'bourse', FLOOR(DATEDIFF(DAY, e.dtbirthdate, aes.dtSessionEnd)/365.242199) AS 'age'
	FROM ENTITYEMP e
	INNER JOIN StudentAdministrativeEnrolment_FOLDER saef ON saef.identityemp = e.identityemp AND saef.IdStudentAdministrativ = '%ID_IA%'
	INNER JOIN studentAdministrativ sa ON sa.IdStudentAdministrativ = saef.IdStudentAdministrativ
	LEFT OUTER JOIN KeyWordValue bourse ON bourse.idKeyWordValue = sa.kwScholarshipHolder
	LEFT OUTER JOIN KeyWordValue kwAffiliation ON kwAffiliation.idKeyWordValue = sa.kwAffiliation
	LEFT OUTER JOIN KeyWordValue kwAffiliation2 ON kwAffiliation2.idKeyWordValue = sa.kwAffiliation2
	LEFT OUTER JOIN KeyWordValue kwForceContribution ON kwForceContribution.idKeyWordValue = sa.kwForceContribution
	INNER JOIN AESessionOfAE_LINK asoal ON asoal.entity1_IdStudentAdministrativ = saef.IdStudentAdministrativ
	INNER JOIN AdminEnrolmentSessio aes ON aes.IdAdminEnrolmentSessio = asoal.entity2_IdAdminEnrolmentSessio
) tmp

UPDATE STUDENTADMINISTRATIV
SET STRADMINENROLMENTNUMBER =
	s.strCode 
	+ '-' 
	+ RIGHT('000' + CAST((
		select COUNT(*) from AESESSIONOFAE_LINK ael1
		left join AESESSIONOFAE_LINK ael2 on ael1.ENTITY2_IDADMINENROLMENTSESSIO = ael2.ENTITY2_IDADMINENROLMENTSESSIO
		inner join STUDENTADMINISTRATIV sa on ael2.ENTITY1_IDSTUDENTADMINISTRATIV = sa.IDSTUDENTADMINISTRATIV
		where ael2.ENTITY1_IDSTUDENTADMINISTRATIV IN (SELECT ENTITY1_IDSTUDENTADMINISTRATIV FROM AESESSIONOFAE_LINK WHERE ID = '%IDLINK%')
		and CAST(STUDENTADMINISTRATIV.CREATEDDATE AS DATE) <= sa.CREATEDDATE 
		AND sa.CREATEDDATE <= STUDENTADMINISTRATIV.CREATEDDATE) AS NVARCHAR(255)), 4)
FROM ADMINENROLMENTSESSIO s
WHERE IDSTUDENTADMINISTRATIV IN (SELECT ENTITY1_IDSTUDENTADMINISTRATIV FROM AESESSIONOFAE_LINK WHERE ID = '%IDLINK%') AND STRADMINENROLMENTNUMBER ='strAdminEnrolmentNumber'

UPDATE STUDENTADMINISTRATIV
SET STRADMINENROLMENTLABEL =
	s.STRNAME 
FROM ADMINENROLMENTSESSIO s
inner join AESESSIONOFAE_LINK ael on ael.ENTITY2_IDADMINENROLMENTSESSIO = s.IDADMINENROLMENTSESSIO

WHERE ael.ENTITY1_IDSTUDENTADMINISTRATIV IN 
(
    SELECT ENTITY1_IDSTUDENTADMINISTRATIV 
    FROM AESESSIONOFAE_LINK 
    WHERE ID = '%IDLINK%'
)

AND IDSTUDENTADMINISTRATIV IN 
(
    SELECT ENTITY1_IDSTUDENTADMINISTRATIV 
    FROM AESESSIONOFAE_LINK 
    WHERE ID = '%IDLINK%'
)

AND STRADMINENROLMENTLABEL = 'strAdminEnrolmentLabel'

									inner join budgetAction_link bal on bal.entity2_idDegree = d.idDegree
